    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[使用python模拟知乎获取二维码登录并保存cookie]]></title>
      <url>/2017/11/19/zhihuLogin/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>最近在学python爬虫，刚学习了模拟知乎登录，于是在这总结一下</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight nix"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#!/usr/bin/env python</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -*- coding: utf-8 -*-</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># @Time    : 2017/11/18 18:01</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># @Author  : luojiandong</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># @File    : zhihu.py</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># @Desc    : 模拟知乎获取二维码登录并保存cookie</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">import</span> json</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">import</span> time</span><br><span class="line">from bs4 <span class="built_in">import</span> BeautifulSoup</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">def zhihuLogin():</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 知乎登录页URL</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">login_url</span> = <span class="string">"https://www.zhihu.com/#signin"</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 知乎POST登录URL</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">url</span> = <span class="string">"https://www.zhihu.com/login/email"</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 使用request构建一个session对象，用来保存cookie</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">sess</span> = requests.Session()</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 自定义headers</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">headers</span> = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"User-Agent"</span>: <span class="string">"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/62.0.3202.75 Safari/537.36"</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 获取登录页html，用于获取_xsrf</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">html</span> = sess.get(login_url, <span class="attr">headers=headers).text</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 使用BeautifulSoup解析html</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">bs</span> = BeautifulSoup(html, <span class="string">"lxml"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 获取_xsrf值</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">_xsrf</span> = bs.find(<span class="string">"input"</span>, <span class="attr">attrs=&#123;"name":</span> <span class="string">"_xsrf"</span>&#125;).get(<span class="string">"value"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 构建验证码url</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">captcha_url</span> = <span class="string">"https://www.zhihu.com/captcha.gif?r=%d&amp;type=login"</span> % int(time.time() * <span class="number">1000</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 获取验证码</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">captcha_data</span> = sess.get(captcha_url, <span class="attr">headers=headers).content</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 写入验证码到本地文件</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">with</span> open(<span class="string">"captcha.jpg"</span>, <span class="string">"wb"</span>) as f:</span><br><span class="line">        f.write(captcha_data)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">text</span> = raw_input(<span class="string">"请输入验证码:"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 构建POST登录form表单</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">captcha_data</span> = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"_xsrf"</span>: _xsrf,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"email"</span>: <span class="string">"952504071@qq.com"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"password"</span>: <span class="string">"517369ljd"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"captcha"</span>: text</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 登录知乎</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">response</span> = sess.post(url, <span class="attr">data=captcha_data,</span> <span class="attr">headers=headers)</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> json.loads(response.text).get(<span class="string">"msg"</span>).encode(<span class="string">"utf8"</span>) == <span class="string">"登录成功"</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        print <span class="string">"使用python模拟知乎登录成功"</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 打开自己主页，验证cookie是否生效</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="attr">__name__</span> == <span class="string">"__main__"</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    zhihuLogin()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
      
